{"tid":1545510,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【和你飛】突發！住東涌同有朋友住東涌既同我入黎！","createTime":"2019-09-06T02:43:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T09:50:37.000Z","uid":270000,"like":247,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"db913179bb18773bf2b31b884ffe23366fbc43ab","tid":1545510,"uid":270000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:43:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">同我like爆呢位「和你飛」！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SRs3rQN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSRs3rQN.jpg&h=2edc76f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E6%96%B9%E9%BE%8D%E9%A3%9B-318421599022887/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E6%2596%25B9%25E9%25BE%258D%25E9%25A3%259B-318421599022887%2F&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H%2FFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=94c7043c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E6%96%B9%E9%BE%8D%E9%A3%9B-318421599022887/</a><br />\n<br />\n上星期日大家被困孤島<br />\n見到呢位阿飛<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">全晚</span><span style=\"color: pink;\">係逸東巴士總站疏導人流</span></span><br />\n<br />\n反之工聯會鄧家彪派喺逸東邨既手下王俊傑<br />\n就一早喺<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">第一次</span>和理飛行動時，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">要求管理處改密碼</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔畀手足避&hellip;&hellip;</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0hHKJtC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0hHKJtC.jpg&h=ea5b6644&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n工賊本身就人人得而誅之，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果比佢選到區議會</span></span>，咁就仆街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（鄧家彪另一個手下劉展鵬就更加失蹤已久）<br />\n<br />\n如果到時呢位阿飛參選，大家請<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">落足十二分力</span></span>叫親朋戚友<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">投佢</span></span>，趕走工賊！！<br />\n<br />\n而家就叫朋友Like左佢先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a043ccb0fc28bbf585cf19b2eb6de3aceb9b9f86","tid":1545510,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:44:20.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4e9f1b545166c58605c7fdb722bd39dc18d126bf","tid":1545510,"uid":207087,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:46:56.000Z","msg":"人渣"},{"pid":"a29fd0e90c7d1a9dacbe8b106931a26a9b05d70e","tid":1545510,"uid":270000,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:48:27.000Z","msg":"push!"},{"pid":"9dadd47abaf19bf1222262146d1d6a7b801fd27a","tid":1545510,"uid":270000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:52:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3215cf2f995ae8241ef6f14b28d7b9104bc8e10f","tid":1545510,"uid":270000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:57:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb3f2432613b581aaffe9870a3a32ca0a69ee517","tid":1545510,"uid":134853,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"db913179bb18773bf2b31b884ffe