/span></span>，趕走工賊！！<br />\n<br />\n而家就叫朋友Like左佢先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:58:53.000Z","msg":"其實我發夢見到有人玩好平小型飛機，幾十元果d,唔知點解下面痴住條銅線，大約1.5米，個尾有個鈎，打橫飛過d電線個鈎就會鈎住最左邊條電線，搭落最右邊條電線度。<br />\n<br />\n好彩電線無開皮，如果好似港鐵d電纜咁，正負一接通實跳掣。"},{"pid":"fbffe792f63395f0c3f7153a5e6ac4d450dddec1","tid":1545510,"uid":270000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:05:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f36151c036e51ba7f73b25a343ede1e8a2860678","tid":1545510,"uid":11223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:10:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f3b43578daf32b472df0b42ba498ec5bdb06032","tid":1545510,"uid":270000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:19:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0a9ceb15a190e1b7a59c798605e814a55a16171","tid":1545510,"uid":305339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:50:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推到工賊選唔到"},{"pid":"c43a48378e402e2e9e7360d71ef703fd1afae4ad","tid":1545510,"uid":270000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0a9ceb15a190e1b7a59c798605e814a55a16171","tid":1545510,"uid":305339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:50:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推到工賊選唔到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T05:06:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"237909a29bae4118a25e2fbbee90bc2653b6b913","tid":1545510,"uid":28444,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T05:07:17.000Z","msg":"逸東二邨好撚深藍，選極都係保皇黨啲人"},{"pid":"96ce778afd87796264a1347d3ff63f4c78b494af","tid":1545510,"uid":195540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":